---
title: American Kumara & Black Bean Enchiladas with Salsa, Greek-Style Yoghurt & Chipotle
description: Thanks to tender roasted chunks of red kumara and carrot, plus hearty black beans, these tasty enchiladas bring their A-game in
every single way.
